                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="console-card-title">Growth & Web Widgets</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="console-card-desc">Deploy responsive floating chat bubbles and click-to-chat QR code plugins on external websites.</p>
