                        <span>Build Widgets</span>
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
